  <head>
    <title>Rpad page</title>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8">
<script type="text/javascript">
    rpadConfig = {
        gui: "alternate"
    };
</script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="gui/dojo.js"></script>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="gui/Rpad.js"></script>
  </head>

  <body>
<p>Enter text here<br></p>

<pre dojoType="Rpad">
# Enter R code here:

</pre>

<p><br></p>
<p><span contenteditable="false"><input onclick="javascript:rpad.calculatePage()" value="Calculate [F9]" type=
      "button"></span>
</p>

<p>The following keys are available:</p>
<ul>
<li>UP & DOWN ARROWS - select blocks up and down</li>
<li>RIGHT ARROW - advance the selection "in" or "down"</li>
<li>LEFT ARROW - move the selection "out"</li>
<li>ENTER - edit the selected block</li>
<li>ESC - finish edits</li>
<li>F9 - calculate page</li>
<li>F8 - calculate section</li>
<li>F7 - calculate section and advance to a new section (Shft-Enter or Ctrl-Enter)</li>
<li>F2 - toggle source view</li>
</ul>                       
  
<p>&nbsp;</p>

  </body>
